[
    {
        "text": "Ramadan is the name of the 9th month of the Islamic moon calendar.",
        "startTime": 17641,
        "endTime": 21529,
        "slowStartTime": 26612,
        "slowEndTime": 32518
    },
    {
        "text": "It is very important because it is the month in which the glorious Koran...",
        "startTime": 22363,
        "endTime": 26240,
        "slowStartTime": 33695,
        "slowEndTime": 39585
    },
    {
        "text": "...was first sent down by Allah to the prophet Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wa Sallam.",
        "startTime": 26471,
        "endTime": 30999,
        "slowStartTime": 39857,
        "slowEndTime": 46724
    },
    {
        "text": "During Ramadan, Muslims must fast...",
        "startTime": 32482,
        "endTime": 34931,
        "slowStartTime": 48873,
        "slowEndTime": 52621
    },
    {
        "text": "...we don't eat or drink between dawn and sunset.",
        "startTime": 35651,
        "endTime": 38285,
        "slowStartTime": 53627,
        "slowEndTime": 57653
    },
    {
        "text": "And we should be very careful to speak and behave in the right way.",
        "startTime": 38913,
        "endTime": 42068,
        "slowStartTime": 58519,
        "slowEndTime": 63327
    },
    {
        "text": "We learn many things from fasting during Ramadan.",
        "startTime": 43701,
        "endTime": 46274,
        "slowStartTime": 65702,
        "slowEndTime": 69636
    },
    {
        "text": "It is a time to increase our remembrance of Allah...",
        "startTime": 47461,
        "endTime": 49864,
        "slowStartTime": 71341,
        "slowEndTime": 75021
    },
    {
        "text": "...and remember the blessings which we have been given.",
        "startTime": 50279,
        "endTime": 52388,
        "slowStartTime": 75568,
        "slowEndTime": 78807
    },
    {
        "text": "We learn how to be thankful for the good things that we normally take for granted.",
        "startTime": 58461,
        "endTime": 62001,
        "slowStartTime": 87842,
        "slowEndTime": 93226
    },
    {
        "text": "After fasting all day, we realize just how wonderful food and drink taste.",
        "startTime": 63485,
        "endTime": 67869,
        "slowStartTime": 95377,
        "slowEndTime": 102029
    },
    {
        "text": "So, we thank Allah more sincerely for providing us with enough to eat and satisfy our thirst.",
        "startTime": 68381,
        "endTime": 73857,
        "slowStartTime": 102721,
        "slowEndTime": 111011
    },
    {
        "text": "Ramadan is a good form of training.",
        "startTime": 75595,
        "endTime": 77869,
        "slowStartTime": 113542,
        "slowEndTime": 117028
    },
    {
        "text": "There may come moments or times in life when things are not easy...",
        "startTime": 79088,
        "endTime": 82417,
        "slowStartTime": 118782,
        "slowEndTime": 123850
    },
    {
        "text": "...and we have to carry on even though it is difficult.",
        "startTime": 82873,
        "endTime": 85055,
        "slowStartTime": 124460,
        "slowEndTime": 127807
    },
    {
        "text": "By fasting, we learn to be patient at such times...",
        "startTime": 86155,
        "endTime": 89376,
        "slowStartTime": 129382,
        "slowEndTime": 134289
    },
    {
        "text": "...and to control ourselves and our bodies.",
        "startTime": 89682,
        "endTime": 91528,
        "slowStartTime": 134673,
        "slowEndTime": 137517
    },
    {
        "text": "This is called self - discipline.",
        "startTime": 92197,
        "endTime": 94005,
        "slowStartTime": 138446,
        "slowEndTime": 141233
    },
    {
        "text": "During this holy month, the prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wa Sallam said,...",
        "startTime": 95969,
        "endTime": 99608,
        "slowStartTime": 144103,
        "slowEndTime": 149637
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"The doors of heaven are opened and the doors of hell closed.\"",
        "startTime": 100967,
        "endTime": 104785,
        "slowStartTime": 151600,
        "slowEndTime": 157403
    },
    {
        "text": "\"And the devils are chained.\"",
        "startTime": 105358,
        "endTime": 106607,
        "slowStartTime": 158187,
        "slowEndTime": 160136
    },
    {
        "text": "This helps us to see ourselves as we really are,...",
        "startTime": 108620,
        "endTime": 110877,
        "slowStartTime": 163080,
        "slowEndTime": 166540
    },
    {
        "text": "...not under the influence of unseen evil forces.",
        "startTime": 111465,
        "endTime": 113863,
        "slowStartTime": 167348,
        "slowEndTime": 171019
    },
    {
        "text": "We can watch and improve ourselves more,...",
        "startTime": 114807,
        "endTime": 116773,
        "slowStartTime": 172361,
        "slowEndTime": 175385
    },
    {
        "text": "...especially by reading the Koran and going to the mosque,...",
        "startTime": 117257,
        "endTime": 120264,
        "slowStartTime": 176036,
        "slowEndTime": 180621
    },
    {
        "text": "...joining in for Tarawih prayers.",
        "startTime": 120688,
        "endTime": 122461,
        "slowStartTime": 181182,
        "slowEndTime": 183917
    },
    {
        "text": "In Ramadan, there is a special night that is better than 1,000 months.",
        "startTime": 134191,
        "endTime": 138935,
        "slowStartTime": 201437,
        "slowEndTime": 208628
    },
    {
        "text": "It is called \"Laylatul Qadr\",...",
        "startTime": 139488,
        "endTime": 141628,
        "slowStartTime": 209382,
        "slowEndTime": 212667
    },
    {
        "text": "...the night in which the Koran was first revealed;...",
        "startTime": 142503,
        "endTime": 145062,
        "slowStartTime": 213905,
        "slowEndTime": 217818
    },
    {
        "text": "...a night in which all our sins can be forgiven.",
        "startTime": 145849,
        "endTime": 149031,
        "slowStartTime": 218923,
        "slowEndTime": 223771
    },
    {
        "text": "Fasting is also important because it makes the rich equal to the poor.",
        "startTime": 157133,
        "endTime": 161263,
        "slowStartTime": 235850,
        "slowEndTime": 242120
    },
    {
        "text": "It gives them a chance to realize what life is like for the less fortunate:...",
        "startTime": 161977,
        "endTime": 165705,
        "slowStartTime": 243115,
        "slowEndTime": 248783
    },
    {
        "text": "...those who have little or no food.",
        "startTime": 165990,
        "endTime": 167633,
        "slowStartTime": 249135,
        "slowEndTime": 251675
    },
    {
        "text": "This helps them become more charitable...",
        "startTime": 168768,
        "endTime": 170613,
        "slowStartTime": 253302,
        "slowEndTime": 256144
    },
    {
        "text": "...and give generously of their wealth to the needy...",
        "startTime": 171145,
        "endTime": 173323,
        "slowStartTime": 256867,
        "slowEndTime": 260209
    },
    {
        "text": "...so that they too can enjoy and share the blessings of Allah...",
        "startTime": 174039,
        "endTime": 177357,
        "slowStartTime": 261208,
        "slowEndTime": 266260
    },
    {
        "text": "...which are enough for all.",
        "startTime": 178009,
        "endTime": 179098,
        "slowStartTime": 267163,
        "slowEndTime": 268872
    }
]